>\n佢付出比我哋任何一個都多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有邊個政棍唔係?</blockquote><br />\n個個都係政棍，個個都唔可以代表你哋，你又唔出去帶領大家？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話佢係政棍好似踩到你條尾咁，真有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cb3fb8f5ddbbbbe40f83d53338c192be4b13a0","tid":363353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:31:18.000Z","msg":"掂晒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20101008/large/09la1p903ru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20101008%2Flarge%2F09la1p903ru.jpg&h=b96ebc7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d38612369c89ce16c836ace046dc699c016e759","tid":363353,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揾人接受左你條女先係首要 你隻死河童根本唔配有女 樣柒矮撚同條女扑野佢都唔爽啦 希望入面班黑懲打到你仆街 等你出黎唔好再利用人上位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到現實中咁撚毒既垃圾係連登可以咁惡"},{"pid":"8952308df4cc4962663ef7a643f673f85a840dd8","tid":363353,"uid":6506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ielts 6.5都好意思拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真心覺得佢好大勇氣</blockquote><br />\n頭段都已經講左佢講野直<br />\n睇佢對答已經佢好識諗"},{"pid":"4ddc1bb395349261d3c5d66c18807945c5a18031","tid":363353,"uid":79237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:48:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2e8ce1e380f4cb3805b65466948332222c97c151","tid":363353,"uid":72730,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:52:03.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒係政棍, 咁又點?<br />\n<br />\n等於佢唔可以同時係政治犯?<br />\n等於中共政治檢控合符社會公義?<br />\n<br />\n我唔認同公民黨, 所以七警就應該打鳩曾健超?<br />\n李波唔係本土派, 所以佢俾人擄走就抵死?<br />\n我為上面兩件事發聲屌柒中共港共, <br />\n就等於我吹奏公民黨, 吹奏李波?"},{"pid":"8bfa7c39e8f22fa4529fccc6861ebe187a4ea4a3","tid":363353,"uid":130745,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:55:53.000Z","msg